OL,7,FThe family of a four-year-old boy who
OL,8,Fdied in the garden of his home have
OL,9,Fpaid tribute to him.
OL,11,FMaldwyn 'Gwern' Evans, died at his
OL,12,Fhome in Tynreithin, Tregaron on
OL,13,FThursday (June 20).
OL,15,FIn a statement released via Dyfed
OL,16,FPowys Police, his family said: "As a
OL,17,Ffamily, we are incredibly distraught
OL,18,Fby our tragic loss, and he will be
OL,19,Fgreatly missed by us and the entire
OL,20,Fcommunity.
