OL,7,F"He was a loving son and a caring
OL,8,Fbrother, who touched the hearts of so
OL,9,Fmany. He lived his short life to the
OL,10,Ffullest and will be remembered for his
OL,11,Fcaptivating personality.
OL,13,F"He was an extremely keen little
OL,14,Ffarmer who had knowledge and ability
OL,15,Fbeyond his years. We would like to
OL,16,Fthank everyone for their support and
OL,17,Fkindness at this horrific time.
